1. Ti *smeješ* se puno i često. (You *laugh* a lot and often.)
2. *Smeješ* se kao da ti je najbolji dan u životu. (*You're laughing* like it's the best day of your life.)
3. Da li se *smeješ* meni ili nečemu drugom? (Are you *laughing* at me or something else?)
4. Kada bih mogao da *smejem* kao ti, moj život bi bio mnogo lepši. (If I could *laugh* like you, my life would be much more beautiful.)
5. Oni nikada ne *smeju* se mom humoru. (They never *laugh* at my jokes.)
6. *Smejala* se tako glasno da su svi okrenuli glavu ka njoj. (*She laughed* so loudly that everyone turned their heads to her.)
7. Moraš da *se smeješ* kako bi održao pozitivan stav u životu. (You have to *laugh* to maintain a positive attitude in life.)
8. Tvoje šale uvek me *nateraju da se smejem*. (Your jokes always *make me laugh*.)
9. Šta si to tako smešno *smejao*? (What were you *laughing* so funny about?)
10. Njen osmeh me *smeje* da se i ja nasmejem. (Her smile *makes me laugh* and I smile too.)